---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="About" description="SynergyCarbon's mission: make carbon credits trustworthy through hardware verification and post-quantum cryptography.">

  <header class="page-hero">
    <h1>About SynergyCarbon</h1>
    <p>
      Making carbon credits trustworthy through hardware verification
      and post-quantum cryptography.
    </p>
  </header>

  <!-- Mission -->
  <section class="section">
    <h2 class="section-title reveal">Our Mission</h2>
    <p class="section-subtitle reveal delay-1">
      Carbon markets suffer from a trust deficit. Credits are issued based on
      self-reported data, verified by infrequent audits, and tracked across
      fragmented registries that can&rsquo;t prevent double-counting.
    </p>

    <div class="detail-grid">
      <div class="detail-card reveal delay-1">
        <h3>The Problem</h3>
        <p>
          Over 90% of rainforest carbon offsets have been found to be worthless
          by independent studies. Manual verification processes, lack of
          real-time monitoring, and siloed registries enable fraud and
          undermine buyer confidence in the entire market.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="detail-card reveal delay-2">
        <h3>Our Approach</h3>
        <p>
          SynergyCarbon replaces trust with verification. Tamper-evident hardware
          nodes witness energy generation at the source. Post-quantum cryptographic
          attestations create an unbreakable chain from physical measurement to
          tradeable credit.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="detail-card reveal delay-3">
        <h3>The Result</h3>
        <p>
          Every carbon credit on SynergyCarbon is backed by hardware-verified
          measurements, quorum-validated calculations, and cross-registry
          deduplication. Buyers get provenance they can verify independently.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Team -->
  <section class="section-surface">
    <div class="section" style="padding-top: 0; padding-bottom: 0;">
      <h2 class="section-title reveal">Leadership Team</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle reveal delay-1">
        Engineers and scientists building the infrastructure for trustworthy carbon markets.
      </p>

      <div class="team-grid">
        <div class="team-card reveal delay-1">
          <div class="team-avatar">&#x1f468;&#x200d;&#x1f4bb;</div>
          <h3>Chief Executive Officer</h3>
          <p>Platform strategy &amp; operations</p>
        </div>
        <div class="team-card reveal delay-2">
          <div class="team-avatar">&#x1f469;&#x200d;&#x1f52c;</div>
          <h3>Chief Technology Officer</h3>
          <p>eStream integration &amp; architecture</p>
        </div>
        <div class="team-card reveal delay-3">
          <div class="team-avatar">&#x1f468;&#x200d;&#x1f3eb;</div>
          <h3>Chief Science Officer</h3>
          <p>Methodology &amp; carbon accounting</p>
        </div>
        <div class="team-card reveal delay-4">
          <div class="team-avatar">&#x1f469;&#x200d;&#x1f4bc;</div>
          <h3>VP of Business Development</h3>
          <p>Partnerships &amp; market expansion</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Partners -->
  <section class="section">
    <h2 class="section-title reveal">Partners &amp; Technology</h2>
    <p class="section-subtitle reveal delay-1">
      Built on industry-leading infrastructure with strategic integration partners.
    </p>

    <div class="detail-grid">
      <div class="detail-card reveal delay-1">
        <h3>ThermogenZero</h3>
        <p>
          First customer and integration partner. ThermogenZero&rsquo;s
          thermoelectric generators are the inaugural energy source on the
          PoVC network, with full witness node deployment and live credit
          minting.
        </p>
        <span class="badge" style="margin-top: 0.75rem;">First Customer</span>
      </div>
      <div class="detail-card reveal delay-2">
        <h3>eStream / PolyQuantum Labs</h3>
        <p>
          The eStream v0.8.3 distributed application platform provides the
          runtime, SmartCircuit compiler, scatter-CAS storage, and
          post-quantum cryptographic primitives that power SynergyCarbon.
        </p>
        <span class="badge" style="margin-top: 0.75rem;">Core Platform</span>
      </div>
      <div class="detail-card reveal delay-3">
        <h3>Registry Partners</h3>
        <p>
          Direct integration bridges with Verra VCS, Gold Standard, CDM,
          and ISCC registries enable cross-platform serial number tracking,
          retirement synchronization, and deduplication.
        </p>
        <span class="badge" style="margin-top: 0.75rem;">4 Registries</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Compliance -->
  <section class="section-dark">
    <div style="max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto;">
      <h2 class="section-title reveal">Compliance &amp; Standards</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle reveal delay-1">
        SynergyCarbon meets or exceeds all major carbon market compliance frameworks.
      </p>

      <div class="advantages-grid">
        <div class="advantage-card reveal delay-1">
          <h3>EPA GHG Reporting</h3>
          <p>
            Compliant with EPA Greenhouse Gas Reporting Program requirements.
            AP-42 emission factors for all applicable source categories.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="advantage-card reveal delay-2">
          <h3>ISO 14064</h3>
          <p>
            Carbon accounting and verification aligned with ISO 14064-1
            (organization level), 14064-2 (project level), and 14064-3
            (validation/verification).
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="advantage-card reveal delay-3">
          <h3>Verra VCS</h3>
          <p>
            Verified Carbon Standard methodology compliance for all supported
            source types. Serial number format, issuance rules, and retirement
            procedures fully integrated.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="advantage-card reveal delay-4">
          <h3>Gold Standard</h3>
          <p>
            Gold Standard for the Global Goals certification pathway with
            sustainable development co-benefit documentation and verification.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="advantage-card reveal delay-5">
          <h3>GHG Protocol</h3>
          <p>
            One-click export to GHG Protocol Corporate Standard and Scope 2/3
            reporting formats. Direct integration with CDP and TCFD
            disclosure frameworks.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="advantage-card reveal delay-1">
          <h3>SOC2 Type II</h3>
          <p>
            Platform security controls aligned with SOC2 Type II requirements.
            Immutable audit log with 10-year retention. Quarterly
            penetration testing.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="section" style="text-align: center;">
    <h2 class="section-title reveal">Join Us</h2>
    <p class="section-subtitle reveal delay-1">
      Partner with us to build trustworthy carbon markets.
    </p>
    <div class="reveal delay-2">
      <a href="/for-developers" class="btn-primary" style="margin-right: 0.75rem;">For Developers</a>
      <a href="/for-buyers" class="btn-outline" style="color: var(--sc-primary-dark); border-color: var(--sc-primary-dark);">For Buyers</a>
    </div>
  </section>

</Base>
